race.comment: UNWORLDLY (1) shapes well for this after finishing second last start over 350m at Healesville but in a scorching 19.00 behind Alston. Has the ability and expected to go close. FLAT OUT FREDDY (3) boasts a strong record this journey with four wins and four minors from 10 tries. In the money last time at The Meadows (29.95) in a Restricted WIN H, finishing a 3.5 lengths third. Looks suited here and can measure up. ZAP DEVERE (2) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fifth (30.74) in a Grade 5 at The Meadows. Form here at the trip sound including two wins. Worth another chance. ZELDA BRAGA (7) has ability and can find the frame.
